


     Required Gnome-Shell Extension:

     1. UNITE ( Remove window titlebar on fullscreen with unity8 style Unity 8 style layout )
        Home Page:https://github.com/hardpixel/unite-shell

     2. BLYR ( Add blur effect Apps & Overview page )
        Home Page: https://github.com/yozoon/gnome-shell-extension-blyr

     3. Workspace to Dash ( for Large Workspace Thumbnail: in the Activities page )
        Home Page: https://github.com/passingthru67/workspaces-to-dock

     4. Activities Configurator ( Customize Activities Button )
        Homepage:  https://nls1729.github.io/activities_config.html
